    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033490/extras/7bcac41732d173c8c2583d7db89ac8a1.webp?t=1724430718\" width=618 height=55 /></span><br>A woman wakes up in a hotel room without any recollection of how she got here. Quickly she notices that she is stuck in there. Can you help her escape the room? And more importantly, find out what happened?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033490/extras/0e99a26db487689a42553f726fad340b.webp?t=1724430718\" width=618 height=55 /></span><br>Follow the mysterious amnesiac protagonist along her journey through the neat paper cut-out world that is a pop-up book! You need to find and combine the proper items to advance. The hotel staff isn’t really helpful, but luckily our main character is breaking the 4th wall every now and then to consult with you. Discover a crime, expose the true criminal and reveal the protagonist’s real identity while you browse through the pages of Hotel Tome!<br><br><strong>This point-and-click adventure provides:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>classic point-and-click puzzles<br></li><li>a neat 2.5D environment in paper aesthetic<br></li><li>fully voiced dialogues<br></li><li>an engaging jazzy soundtrack<br></li><li>stupid and funny interactions!<br></li><li>and a plot twist you surely didn’t see coming …</li></ul>",
